         Data will be provided to ``parse`` which should invoke
         @:meth:`GstVideo.VideoDecoder.add_to_frame` and @:meth:`GstVideo.VideoDecoder.have_frame` to
         separate the data belonging to each video frame.

      * Accept data in ``handle_frame`` and provide decoded results to
         @:meth:`GstVideo.VideoDecoder.finish_frame`, or call @:meth:`GstVideo.VideoDecoder.drop_frame`.
